Package: sony-head-tracker
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
 libgtk-4-1, libadwaita-1-0, python3, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1
Recommends: opentrack
Description: head tracking from Sony headphones for OpenTrack
 Turns compatible Sony Bluetooth headphones into a real-time head tracker for
 OpenTrack and other applications, with a command-line bridge and a GTK app.
 It reads the Android Head Tracker HID sensor the headset exposes and streams
 yaw/pitch/roll over loopback UDP. Linux port of Nicholas Slattery's Sony Head
 Tracker.
